==English==
===Alternative spellings===
'''son-of-a-bitch''', '''sonofabitch'''
===Noun===
'''son of a bitch''' (''plural'' '''[[sons of bitches]]''')

#(''derogatory taboo slang'') An objectionable person.
#(''derogatory taboo slang'') Any objectionable thing.
#:''"This son of a bitch won’t move!" Marty exclaimed as he grappled with the supermarket cart.''

